Unification with "triangular substitutions" (i.e. in accumulator-passing
style), inspired by the Scheme implementation used in miniKanren.

For more details, see the paper:
(Nominal) Unification by Recursive Descent with Triangular Substitutions
Ramana Kumar and Michael Norrish
ITP 2010, pp 51-66
http://dx.doi.org/10.1007/978-3-642-14052-5_6
